        "remove_vertical_spacing": false,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "<!-- ===== COMPARATIF ===== -->\n<div class=\"rlv-cmp\">\n  <div class=\"rlv-cmp__left\">\n    <h2 class=\"rlv-cmp__h2\">Toutes les solutions<br><span>ne se valent pas.</span></h2>\n    <p class=\"rlv-cmp__sub\">La plupart traitent la douleur. FELINO traite la cause.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"rlv-cmp__table\">\n    <div class=\"rlv-cmp__row rlv-cmp__row--head\">\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c1\"></div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c2 rlv-cmp__c2--top\">\n        <span class=\"rlv-cmp__brand\">felino</span>\n        <span class=\"rlv-cmp__badge\">Technologie Orthobionale</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c3\">\n        <strong>Autres<br>solutions</strong>\n        <small>Injections de cortisone, physiothérapie & massages</small>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rlv-cmp__row\">\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c1\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#7a8088\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"/><path d=\"M12 7v5l3 2\"/></svg>Solution durable</div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c2\"><span class=\"rlv-cmp__ok\">✓</span></div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c3\"><span class=\"rlv-cmp__ko\">✕</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rlv-cmp__row\">\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c1\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#7a8088\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 4 13c0-5 4-9 8-11 4 2 8 6 8 11a7 7 0 0 1-7 7Z\"/><path d=\"M11 20v-7\"/></svg>Aucun effet secondaire</div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c2\"><span class=\"rlv-cmp__ok\">✓</span></div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c3\"><span class=\"rlv-cmp__ko\">✕</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rlv-cmp__row\">\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c1\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#7a8088\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-7 8-13a8 8 0 1 0-16 0c0 6 8 13 8 13Z\"/><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"9\" r=\"2.5\"/></svg>Développé en Allemagne</div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c2\"><span class=\"rlv-cmp__ok\">✓</span></div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c3\"><span class=\"rlv-cmp__ko\">✕</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rlv-cmp__row\">\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c1\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#7a8088\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M12 2 4 5v7c0 5 3.5 8.5 8 10 4.5-1.5 8-5 8-10V5l-8-3Z\"/><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"/></svg>Garantie satisfait ou remboursé 60 jours</div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c2\"><span class=\"rlv-cmp__ok\">✓</span></div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c3\"><span class=\"rlv-cmp__ko\">✕</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rlv-cmp__row\">\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c1\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#7a8088\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"/><path d=\"M14.5 9.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-5 0c0 1.5 1 2 2.5 2.5s2.5 1 2.5 2.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-5 0M12 7v10\"/></svg>Coût unique faible</div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c2 rlv-cmp__c2--bot\"><span class=\"rlv-cmp__ok\">✓</span></div>\n      <div class=\"rlv-cmp__c3\"><span class=\"rlv-cmp__ko\">✕</span></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- ===== ÉTAPES ===== -->\n<div class=\"rlv-steps\">\n  <h2 class=\"rlv-steps__title\">Aussi simple <span>que ça</span></h2>\n  <div class=\"rlv-steps__grid\">\n    <div class=\"rlv-steps__card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1001/9337/0459/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_crtnxdcrtnxdcrtn_1_png_ca9c42ab-b6b8-4da2-8208-e6a8665f23f1.png?v=1778687117\" alt=\"Étape 1\">\n      <h3>Étape 1 :</h3>\n      <p>Charge complètement l'appareil</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rlv-steps__card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1001/9337/0459/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_wfc0r1wfc0r1wfc0_1_png.png?v=1778687117\" alt=\"Étape 2\">\n      <h3>Étape 2 :</h3>\n      <p>Place l'appareil sur ton épaule et passe la sangle autour de ton corps</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rlv-steps__card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1001/9337/0459/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_d0earcd0earcd0ea_2_png.png?v=1778687117\" alt=\"Étape 3\">\n      <h3>Étape 3 :</h3>\n      <p>Allume l'appareil et ressens la technologie Orthobionale faire disparaître tes douleurs</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rlv-steps__card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1001/9337/0459/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_1yc54k1yc54k1yc5_1_png.png?v=1778687117\" alt=\"Étape 4\">\n      <h3>Étape 4 :</h3>\n      <p>Sens-toi libre, reposé et plein d'énergie</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n/* Comparatif */\n.rlv-cmp{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:60px 20px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.3fr;gap:40px;align-items:center;font-family:inherit}\n.rlv-cmp__h2{font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,38px);font-weight:800;margin:0 0 16px;color:#111;line-height:1.2}\n.rlv-cmp__h2 span{color:#2aa37a}\n.rlv-cmp__sub{font-size:15px;color:#444;margin:0;line-height:1.6}\n.rlv-cmp__table{display:flex;flex-direction:column}\n.rlv-cmp__row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.5fr 1fr 1fr;align-items:center;border-bottom:1px solid #eaeaea}\n.rlv-cmp__row:last-child{border-bottom:0}\n.rlv-cmp__row--head{border-bottom:0;align-items:stretch}\n.rlv-cmp__c1{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:14px 10px;font-size:14px;color:#222;font-weight:500}\n.rlv-cmp__c1 svg{width:22px;height:22px;flex-shrink:0}\n.rlv-cmp__c2{background:#2aa37a;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:14px 10px;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;color:#fff;text-align:center}\n.rlv-cmp__c2--top{border-radius:60px 60px 0 0;padding:22px 10px 14px}\n.rlv-cmp__c2--bot{border-radius:0 0 60px 60px;padding:14px 10px 22px}\n.rlv-cmp__brand{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;text-transform:lowercase}\n.rlv-cmp__badge{font-size:11px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.18);color:#fff;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:600}\n.rlv-cmp__c3{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:14px 10px;text-align:center;gap:4px}\n.rlv-cmp__row--head .rlv-cmp__c3 strong{font-size:15px;color:#111}\n.rlv-cmp__row--head .rlv-cmp__c3 small{font-size:11px;color:#666;line-height:1.3}\n.rlv-cmp__ok{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff;color:#2aa37a;font-weight:900;font-size:14px}\n.rlv-cmp__ko{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;background:#111;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:13px}\n@media (max-width:768px){.rlv-cmp{grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center}.rlv-cmp__left{text-align:center}}\n\n/* Étapes */\n.rlv-steps{max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;padding:30px 20px 60px;font-family:inherit}\n.rlv-steps__title{text-align:center;font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,34px);font-weight:800;color:#111;margin:0 0 40px}\n.rlv-steps__title span{color:#2aa37a}\n.rlv-steps__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:20px}\n.rlv-steps__card{border:1px solid #eaeaea;border-radius:14px;padding:14px;background:#fff}\n.rlv-steps__card img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:1/1;object-fit:cover;border-radius:10px;display:block;margin-bottom:18px}\n.rlv-steps__card h3{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#111}\n.rlv-steps__card p{margin:0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#444}\n@media (max-width:1024px){.rlv-steps__grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}\n@media (max-width:560px){.rlv-steps__grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}\n</style>",
